parameters.body/body/messageBody:
{
  "$schema": "http://adaptivecards.io/schemas/adaptive-card.json",
  "type": "AdaptiveCard",
  "version": "1.4",
  "body": [
    {
      "type": "Container",
      "style": "emphasis",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "TextBlock",
          "text": "Solicitacao de Ferias",
          "weight": "Bolder",
          "size": "Large",
          "color": "Accent"
        },
        {
          "type": "TextBlock",
          "text": "Aprovacao pendente",
          "spacing": "None",
          "isSubtle": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "FactSet",
      "facts": [
        {
          "title": "Colaborador:",
          "value": "@{first(outputs('GetEmployeeDetails')?['body/value'])?['NomeCompleto']}"
        },
        {
          "title": "E-mail:",
          "value": "@{variables('varEmployeeEmail')}"
        },
        {
          "title": "Periodo:",
          "value": "@{formatDateTime(triggerOutputs()?['body/DataInicio'], 'dd/MM/yyyy')} a @{formatDateTime(triggerOutputs()?['body/DataFim'], 'dd/MM/yyyy')}"
        },
        {
          "title": "Total de dias:",
          "value": "@{triggerOutputs()?['body/DiasUteis']} dias uteis"
        },
        {
          "title": "Observacoes:",
          "value": "@{triggerOutputs()?['body/Observacoes']}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "TextBlock",
      "text": "Comentario (opcional):",
      "weight": "Bolder",
      "spacing": "Medium"
    },
    {
      "type": "Input.Text",
      "id": "comments",
      "placeholder": "Adicione um comentario...",
      "isMultiline": true,
      "maxLength": 500
    }
  ],
  "actions": [
    {
      "type": "Action.Submit",
      "title": "Aprovar",
      "style": "positive",
      "data": {
        "action": "approve"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "Action.Submit",
      "title": "Rejeitar",
      "style": "destructive",
      "data": {
        "action": "reject"
      }
    }
  ]
}

parameters.body/messageBody:
Suas ferias foram APROVADAS!

Periodo: @{formatDateTime(triggerOutputs()?['body/DataInicio'], 'dd/MM/yyyy')} a @{formatDateTime(triggerOutputs()?['body/DataFim'], 'dd/MM/yyyy')}
Total: @{triggerOutputs()?['body/DiasUteis']} dias

Aprovado por: @{variables('varApproverEmail')}

Sua solicitacao de ferias foi REJEITADA.

Periodo solicitado: @{formatDateTime(triggerOutputs()?['body/DataInicio'], 'dd/MM/yyyy')} a @{formatDateTime(triggerOutputs()?['body/DataFim'], 'dd/MM/yyyy')}
Motivo: @{body('PostApprovalCard')?['data']?['comments']}

Entre em contato com seu gestor para mais informacoes.
